        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2772645/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2772645-5.jpg" alt="白菜" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12667564/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12667564/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2772645/" class=" " title="白菜">白菜</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12667564">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们（不能）在我们的行为尚未为我们挣得幸福之时就要求幸福；
唯有善人才是幸福的；
诸神之所以是幸福的，只是因为他们是善的。

		普罗提诺：《九章集》III，2，4</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-05-04 02:58</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
